data.description: This is a very well-maintained concrete house with 3 bedrooms and 2 baths on a .34-acre lot completely fenced. in a nice community. There is tile throughout the property. You will love the kitchen with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. Include washer and dryer, light fixtures. The A/C unit is around 4 years old. The enclosed Florida Room also has a wall unit A/C and can be used as a flex room. You can't miss this one! Approximately 3 miles away from Walmart, 4 miles from a health services clinic, 1 mile away from Lake Weir High School, and 6 miles away from Lake Weir, where you and your family can spend some relaxing time by the lake and restaurants. Enjoy the tranquility of the area while being conveniently close to local amenities. Explore the beauty of Ocala from the comfort of this inviting residence. Schedule your showing today
